{
    "title": "Samba do buraco do metrô",
    "artist": "Lello Di Sarno",
    "composer": "Lello Di Sarno/Bi/Tico Macumba",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Nem queira saber o quanto você me machucou</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O buraco que você em meu peito deixou</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Foi maior que o da linha quatro do metrô</span>\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>                                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Você não gosta de mim estou careca de saber</span>\n             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>                                            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mais careca que o nosso governador</span>\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>                              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O que me falta em carinho também me falta em dinheiro</span>\n                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Fui abandonado ao lado da estação Pinheiros</span>\n                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Fui abandonado ao lado da estação Pinheiros</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Nem queira saber…</span>\n\n           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>                                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Você nunca me amou vou procurar amparo</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>                                              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E fazer baldeação em Santo Amaro</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A minha casa está rachada, o meu coração também</span>\n                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Daqui pra frente só vou viajar de trem</span>\n                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Daqui pra frente só vou viajar de trem</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ô ô ô ô ô ô</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O trem ta atrasado ou já passou*</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">* música incidental:</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Samba do crioulo doido, Stanislaw Ponte Preta</span>\n",
